member.name: Windows.HPALETTE_UserMarshal

member.name: Windows.HPALETTE_UserSize
member.summary: Calculates the wire size of the HPALETTE object and gets its handle and data. (HPALETTE_UserSize)
member.param: The current buffer offset where the object will be marshaled. The method has to account for any padding needed for the HPALETTE object to be properly aligned when it will be marshaled to the buffer.
member.returns: A LONG value expressing the size of the object.
